To: Nick Palmer <nicholas(-at-)brigadoon.slackers.net>
Subject: Re: [T2] Broken lock...

Replace the lock cylinder with a used one.  Switch your wafers to
the new cylinder and you'll keep the same keying.

Fix the latch mechinism (probably a little missing spring) to prevent
overstressing the cylinder.

George



